    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results for pressure head, velocity field, and wall shear stress include structured uncertainty quantification. The hemolysis index validation result documents inherent biological variability qualitatively; this was reviewed by the assessment team and judged sufficient for the Medium assurance level decision. RH < 1.0 across all operating points confirms the model satisfies the COU acceptance criterion. The overall credibility package supports the Accepted decision for this Class II CPB device submission.",
